1. *Greška* je bila naša. (The mistake was ours.)
2. Učinio je veliku *grešku*. (He made a big mistake.)
3. Uvek se trudim da ne bih napravio *grešku*. (I always try not to make a mistake.) 
4. On nije priznao *grešku*. (He didn't admit his mistake.)
5. *Greške* se dešavaju. (Mistakes happen.)
6. Nisam mogao da izbegnem *grešku*. (I couldn't avoid the mistake.) 
7. On je učinio *grešku*. (He did a mistake.)